  "vulnerability_information": "I reported this vulnerability through the official Apache HTTP Server security email on 2024-07-12, and received a CVE number on 2024-07-17. You can check detailed information from here:\nhttps://httpd.apache.org/security/vulnerabilities_24.html\n\n## Impact\n\nSSRF in Apache HTTP Server on Windows with mod_rewrite in server/vhost context, allows to potentially leak NTLM hashes to a malicious server via SSRF and malicious requests.",
